          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "The ruins of Annuminas were at one time the greatest libraries of the ancient realm of Arthedain. Arthedian like Annuminas was beseiged by The Dark Lord Saurons cheif lieutenant, The Witch King. The Witch King, a foul ringwraith dessemated this land around 1,000 years ago."
