        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "The Witch King laid these lands barren long ago, and has since moved on to other business I assume. Only recently Gondor sent our expidition to Annuminas to attempt to recover some of the ancient tomes of wisdon of its age."
